      <description>&lt;p&gt;Prynth are programmable sound synthesizers powered by single-board computers. They combine the advantages of dedicated hardware with the flexibility of programming.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This project&amp;rsquo;s goal is to develop a set of free technologies and guides for instrument assembly, while fostering knowledge exchange and discussion between creators.&lt;/p&gt;
